commit.message:
Add structured logging with pino across all backend apps

Replace 51 console.* calls with pino-based structured logging. New shared
@clawbada/logger package provides a factory and Hono middleware. JSON output
in production, pino-pretty in development. Each app creates a service logger;
modules use .child() for context (module, contract, battleId, etc.).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
